Interface Game

All Known Implementing Classes:
GameOfLife
public interface Game

An interface for implementations of variants of Conway's Game of Life.

Your GameOfLife class will implement this interface. Your GameOfLife class will have a TwoDBoard instance field (member data). When you instantiate the TwoDBoard, you will call the GameOfLifeBoard constructor.

Author:
sm053
